OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNigeria rebukes states for 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fquitting regional bloc     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Nigeria has accused Mali, Burkina Faso 
OL,6, and Niger of letting their people down 
OL,7, by quitting the Economic Community of  
OL,8, West African States (Ecowas).          
OL,10,FIt is the first comment from the chair 
OL,11,Fof the economic and political body     
OL,12,Fsince the three governments announced  
OL,13,Ftheir decision to leave on Sunday.     
OL,15,FThe three states were already suspended
OL,16,Ffrom Ecowas after recent coups.        
OL,18,FTheir military rulers have distanced   
OL,19,Fthemselves from ex-colonial power      
OL,20,FFrance and strengthened ties to Russia.
